ygData.messageBody:
I've been too busy playing EQ to check my email so I'm late responding to
this.
This type of spam is NOT allowed on this mailing list. If you want to sell
your character, don't do it here.
Read the rules for the list. I will not allow anything that violates the
User Liscense Agreement for EQ.
There is no excuse to not read the rules of the list. Anyone who posts these
types of messages will be banned immediately.
-Su (List Owner)

> This is an auction for the sell of an everquest account. I have
> the characters spread on Ayonae Ro and Cazic-Thule servers. The 52
> iksar monk has his epic weapon, sash of the dragonborn, embued
> fighters staff, pantherskin, and fbss just to name a few items. He
> is full decked out in high end items, quest gear, planar gear, ect.
> The 59 dark elf necro almost has his epic, all spells up to 59 and
> some 60 spells. He has alot of quest and planar gear on. Both of
> these are on Cazic-Thule server.
> The 47 druid is on Ayonae ro, doesnt have much. Has all his
> spells, and testament of vanear. There are about 10 other characters
> ranging from 5-35 on the servers. The monk has about 100k worth of
> gear on him and in the bank.
> highest bidder wins on the day of 10/17/02. Any questions, email
> me at muggishmann@...
>
